  "detailed_description": "<strong>Place tiles on the board to match the color or symbol of adjacent tiles to create 'passages' from edge to edge.</strong> Completed rows and columns ('passages') disappear from the board. Passage 4 is an easy to learn but challenging game that incorporates the best elements of several classic games. It will keep you fascinated for hours. Give it a try!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>More than 220 levels \t<br></li><li>3 game modes with 3 levels of difficulty \t<br></li><li>6 different graphic themes \t<br></li><li>Spoken tutorial\t<br></li><li>Great sound effects and background music</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/567860/extras/b32199acd4041058c372441dd3426aef.avif?t=1682593948\" width=800 height=150 /></span>",
